profile:
Premiere Van Lines Calgary, formally known as Classic Moving & Storage Ltd. has been operating as a moving company within Calgary for over 35 years. As evidence of their continual emphasis on improving customer service they have been the recipient of numerous Regional Western Canada and National Quality Service Awards from Atlas Van Lines. Our Calgary movers move large global companies to individual homes and apartments. Regardless of the size of the move they provide everyone with the highest quality of service. Contact us to receive a free estimate for your home, show homes, or business today.

Premiere provides efficient and on time local, long distance, international and office moves.  We do this by minimizing downtime and focusing on getting you into your new home as quick as possible.  Our bonded and uniformed movers are professionally trained, background checked, and use equipment that is regularly cleaned and maintained.  

At Premiere we provide capable and functional teams of household & commercial movers that will take care of all your needs.
